{"tid":873062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"印tee有咩要注意?","createTime":"2018-10-23T07:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T08:14:56.000Z","uid":87064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"00964055ef43544a986e77a0e9e291946096d08c","tid":873062,"uid":87064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:14:09.000Z","msg":"我想喺香港印件自己做簡單設計既tee<br />\n正面背面都有少少野要印<br />\n但我對印tee既基本認識得1%<br />\n我見料 同埋印既方法都有好多種<br />\n有冇試過印tee既巴絲可以指點迷津<br />\n<br />\n例如邊隻料最好 唔同既印法有咩分別 因為睇網上既圖真係唔多睇得出<br />\n<br />\n或者可以分享成功/中伏經驗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa53f698cfcba6314ab033a7fc8e692c362c7055","tid":873062,"uid":87064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071b6f1259c75258b88774f4555993e4d4c6ca66","tid":873062,"uid":193738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T07:40:39.000Z","msg":"打電話去啲公司到問啦 中學生都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7734833ce4b94213c79d12c9d8c18371d13683","tid":873062,"uid":87064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}